des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
Often, you find the homeless begging for money with cardboard hoardings, but could this be turned into a guerilla marketing idea for products, endorsed by homeless people carry placard ads? Listen on to this funny story about guerilla marketing and innovation, maybe it is a new chapter in data mining.
